{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So that's Johnny Depp, of course."},{"time":4000,"text":"And that's Johnny Depp's shoulder."},{"time":7000,"text":"And that's Johnny Depp's famous shoulder tattoo."},{"time":11000,"text":"Some of you might know that, in 1990,"},{"time":13000,"text":"Depp got engaged to Winona Ryder,"},{"time":15000,"text":"and he had tattooed on his right shoulder"},{"time":17000,"text":"\"Winona forever.\""},{"time":20000,"text":"And then three years later --"},{"time":22000,"text":"which in fairness, kind of is forever by Hollywood standards --"},{"time":25000,"text":"they broke up,"},{"time":27000,"text":"and Johnny went and got a little bit of repair work done."},{"time":29000,"text":"And now his shoulder says, \"Wino forever.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"So like Johnny Depp,"},{"time":38000,"text":"and like 25 percent of Americans"},{"time":40000,"text":"between the ages of 16 and 50,"},{"time":44000,"text":"I have a tattoo."},{"time":47000,"text":"I first started thinking about getting it in my mid-20s,"},{"time":50000,"text":"but I deliberately waited a really long time."},{"time":53000,"text":"Because we all know people"},{"time":55000,"text":"who have gotten tattoos when they were 17"},{"time":57000,"text":"or 19 or 23"},{"time":59000,"text":"and regretted it by the time they were 30."},{"time":63000,"text":"That didn't happen to me."},{"time":66000,"text":"I got my tattoo when I was 29,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and I regretted it instantly."},{"time":72000,"text":"And by \"regretted it,\""},{"time":74000,"text":"I mean that I stepped outside of the tattoo place --"},{"time":77000,"text":"this is just a couple miles from here"},{"time":79000,"text":"down on the Lower East Side --"},{"time":81000,"text":"and I had a massive emotional meltdown in broad daylight"},{"time":84000,"text":"on the corner of East Broadway and Canal Street."},{"time":86000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":88000,"text":"Which is a great place to do it because nobody cares."},{"time":90000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":92000,"text":"And then I went home that night, and I had an even larger emotional meltdown,"},{"time":95000,"text":"which I'll say more about in a minute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"And this was all actually quite shocking to me,"},{"time":100000,"text":"because prior to this moment,"},{"time":102000,"text":"I had prided myself"},{"time":104000,"text":"on having absolutely no regrets."},{"time":106000,"text":"I made a lot of mistakes"},{"time":108000,"text":"and dumb decisions, of course."},{"time":110000,"text":"I do that hourly."},{"time":112000,"text":"But I had always felt like, look, you know,"},{"time":115000,"text":"I made the best choice I could make"},{"time":117000,"text":"given who I was then,"},{"time":119000,"text":"given the information I had on hand."},{"time":121000,"text":"I learned a lesson from it."},{"time":123000,"text":"It somehow got me to where I am in life right now."},{"time":125000,"text":"And okay, I wouldn't change it."},{"time":130000,"text":"In other words, I had drunk our great cultural Kool-Aid about regret,"},{"time":134000,"text":"which is that lamenting things that occurred in the past"},{"time":137000,"text":"is an absolute waste of time,"},{"time":139000,"text":"that we should always look forward and not backward,"},{"time":142000,"text":"and that one of the noblest and best things we can do"},{"time":144000,"text":"is strive to live a life free of regrets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147000,"text":"This idea is nicely captured by this quote:"},{"time":150000,"text":"\"Things without all remedy"},{"time":152000,"text":"should be without regard;"},{"time":155000,"text":"what's done is done.\""},{"time":157000,"text":"And it seems like kind of an admirable philosophy at first --"},{"time":160000,"text":"something we might all agree to sign onto ..."},{"time":163000,"text":"until I tell you who said it."},{"time":167000,"text":"Right, so this is Lady MacBeth"},{"time":169000,"text":"basically telling her husband to stop being such a wuss"},{"time":172000,"text":"for feeling bad about murdering people."},{"time":175000,"text":"And as it happens, Shakespeare was onto something here,"},{"time":178000,"text":"as he generally was."},{"time":180000,"text":"Because the inability to experience regret"},{"time":183000,"text":"is actually one of the diagnostic characteristics"},{"time":185000,"text":"of sociopaths."},{"time":188000,"text":"It's also, by the way, a characteristic of certain kinds of brain damage."},{"time":191000,"text":"So people who have damage"},{"time":193000,"text":"to their orbital frontal cortex"},{"time":195000,"text":"seem to be unable to feel regret"},{"time":197000,"text":"in the face of even obviously very poor decisions."},{"time":201000,"text":"So if, in fact, you want to live a life free of regret,"},{"time":203000,"text":"there is an option open to you."},{"time":206000,"text":"It's called a lobotomy."},{"time":209000,"text":"But if you want to be fully functional"},{"time":211000,"text":"and fully human"},{"time":213000,"text":"and fully humane,"},{"time":216000,"text":"I think you need to learn to live, not without regret, but with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"So let's start off by defining some terms."},{"time":221000,"text":"What is regret?"},{"time":223000,"text":"Regret is the emotion we experience"},{"time":225000,"text":"when we think that our present situation"},{"time":227000,"text":"could be better or happier"},{"time":229000,"text":"if we had done something different in the past."},{"time":231000,"text":"So in other words, regret requires two things."},{"time":233000,"text":"It requires, first of all, agency -- we had to make a decision in the first place."},{"time":236000,"text":"And second of all, it requires imagination."},{"time":239000,"text":"We need to be able to imagine going back and making a different choice,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and then we need to be able to kind of spool this imaginary record forward"},{"time":245000,"text":"and imagine how things would be playing out in our present."},{"time":249000,"text":"And in fact, the more we have of either of these things --"},{"time":251000,"text":"the more agency and the more imagination"},{"time":254000,"text":"with respect to a given regret,"},{"time":256000,"text":"the more acute that regret will be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259000,"text":"So let's say for instance"},{"time":261000,"text":"that you're on your way to your best friend's wedding"},{"time":263000,"text":"and you're trying to get to the airport and you're stuck in terrible traffic,"},{"time":266000,"text":"and you finally arrive at your gate"},{"time":268000,"text":"and you've missed your flight."},{"time":270000,"text":"You're going to experience more regret in that situation"},{"time":272000,"text":"if you missed your flight by three minutes"},{"time":274000,"text":"than if you missed it by 20."},{"time":277000,"text":"Why?"},{"time":279000,"text":"Well because, if you miss your flight by three minutes,"},{"time":281000,"text":"it is painfully easy to imagine"},{"time":283000,"text":"that you could have made different decisions"},{"time":285000,"text":"that would have led to a better outcome."},{"time":287000,"text":"\"I should have taken the bridge and not the tunnel."},{"time":289000,"text":"I should have gone through that yellow light.\""},{"time":292000,"text":"These are the classic conditions that create regret."},{"time":295000,"text":"We feel regret when we think we are responsible"},{"time":298000,"text":"for a decision that came out badly,"},{"time":300000,"text":"but almost came out well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303000,"text":"Now within that framework,"},{"time":305000,"text":"we can obviously experience regret about a lot of different things."},{"time":308000,"text":"This session today is about behavioral economics."},{"time":311000,"text":"And most of what we know about regret"},{"time":314000,"text":"comes to us out of that domain."},{"time":316000,"text":"We have a vast body of literature"},{"time":319000,"text":"on consumer and financial decisions"},{"time":321000,"text":"and the regrets associated with them --"},{"time":323000,"text":"buyer's remorse, basically."},{"time":325000,"text":"But then finally, it occurred to some researchers to step back"},{"time":328000,"text":"and say, well okay, but overall,"},{"time":330000,"text":"what do we regret most in life?"},{"time":333000,"text":"Here's what the answers turn out to look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335000,"text":"So top six regrets --"},{"time":337000,"text":"the things we regret most in life:"},{"time":339000,"text":"Number one by far, education."},{"time":341000,"text":"33 percent of all of our regrets"},{"time":343000,"text":"pertain to decisions we made about education."},{"time":345000,"text":"We wish we'd gotten more of it."},{"time":347000,"text":"We wish we'd taken better advantage of the education that we did have."},{"time":350000,"text":"We wish we'd chosen to study a different topic."},{"time":353000,"text":"Others very high on our list of regrets"},{"time":355000,"text":"include career, romance, parenting,"},{"time":358000,"text":"various decisions and choices about our sense of self"},{"time":361000,"text":"and how we spend our leisure time --"},{"time":363000,"text":"or actually more specifically,"},{"time":365000,"text":"how we fail to spend our leisure time."},{"time":367000,"text":"The remaining regrets"},{"time":369000,"text":"pertain to these things:"},{"time":371000,"text":"finance, family issues unrelated to romance or parenting,"},{"time":374000,"text":"health, friends,"},{"time":376000,"text":"spirituality and community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379000,"text":"So in other words, we know most of what we know about regret"},{"time":382000,"text":"by the study of finance."},{"time":384000,"text":"But it turns out, when you look overall at what people regret in life,"},{"time":386000,"text":"you know what, our financial decisions don't even rank."},{"time":389000,"text":"They account for less than three percent of our total regrets."},{"time":393000,"text":"So if you're sitting there stressing"},{"time":395000,"text":"about large cap versus small cap,"},{"time":397000,"text":"or company A versus company B,"},{"time":399000,"text":"or should you buy the Subaru or the Prius,"},{"time":401000,"text":"you know what, let it go."},{"time":404000,"text":"Odds are, you're not going to care in five years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407000,"text":"But for these things that we actually do really care about"},{"time":410000,"text":"and do experience profound regret around,"},{"time":412000,"text":"what does that experience feel like?"},{"time":416000,"text":"We all know the short answer."},{"time":418000,"text":"It feels terrible. Regret feels awful."},{"time":420000,"text":"But it turns out that regret feels awful"},{"time":422000,"text":"in four very specific and consistent ways."},{"time":425000,"text":"So the first consistent component of regret"},{"time":427000,"text":"is basically denial."},{"time":430000,"text":"When I went home that night after getting my tattoo,"},{"time":433000,"text":"I basically stayed up all night."},{"time":435000,"text":"And for the first several hours,"},{"time":437000,"text":"there was exactly one thought in my head."},{"time":439000,"text":"And the thought was,"},{"time":441000,"text":"\"Make it go away!\""},{"time":444000,"text":"This is an unbelievably primitive emotional response."},{"time":448000,"text":"I mean, it's right up there with, \"I want my mommy!\""},{"time":451000,"text":"We're not trying to solve the problem."},{"time":453000,"text":"We're not trying to understand how the problem came about."},{"time":456000,"text":"We just want it to vanish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459000,"text":"The second characteristic component of regret"},{"time":461000,"text":"is a sense of bewilderment."},{"time":463000,"text":"So the other thing I thought about there in my bedroom that night"},{"time":466000,"text":"was, \"How could I have done that?"},{"time":469000,"text":"What was I thinking?\""},{"time":472000,"text":"This real sense of alienation"},{"time":474000,"text":"from the part of us that made a decision we regret."},{"time":476000,"text":"We can't identify with that part."},{"time":478000,"text":"We don't understand that part."},{"time":480000,"text":"And we certainly don't have any empathy for that part --"},{"time":482000,"text":"which explains the third consistent component of regret,"},{"time":485000,"text":"which is an intense desire to punish ourselves."},{"time":487000,"text":"That's why, in the face of our regret,"},{"time":489000,"text":"the thing we consistently say is, \"I could have kicked myself.\""},{"time":493000,"text":"The fourth component here"},{"time":495000,"text":"is that regret is what psychologists call perseverative."},{"time":497000,"text":"To perseverate means to focus obsessively and repeatedly"},{"time":500000,"text":"on the exact same thing."},{"time":502000,"text":"Now the effect of perseveration"},{"time":504000,"text":"is to basically take these first three components of regret"},{"time":506000,"text":"and put them on an infinite loop."},{"time":509000,"text":"So it's not that I sat there in my bedroom that night,"},{"time":512000,"text":"thinking, \"Make it go away.\""},{"time":515000,"text":"It's that I sat there and I thought,"},{"time":517000,"text":"\"Make it go away. Make it go away."},{"time":519000,"text":"Make it go away. Make it go away.\""},{"time":522000,"text":"So if you look at the psychological literature,"},{"time":524000,"text":"these are the four consistent defining components of regret."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528000,"text":"But I want to suggest that there's also a fifth one."},{"time":531000,"text":"And I think of this"},{"time":533000,"text":"as a kind of existential wake-up call."},{"time":536000,"text":"That night in my apartment,"},{"time":538000,"text":"after I got done kicking myself and so forth,"},{"time":541000,"text":"I lay in bed for a long time,"},{"time":543000,"text":"and I thought about skin grafts."},{"time":547000,"text":"And then I thought about how,"},{"time":549000,"text":"much as travel insurance doesn't cover acts of God,"},{"time":552000,"text":"probably my health insurance did not cover acts of idiocy."},{"time":557000,"text":"In point of fact, no insurance covers acts of idiocy."},{"time":560000,"text":"The whole point of acts of idiocy"},{"time":562000,"text":"is that they leave you totally uninsured;"},{"time":564000,"text":"they leave you exposed to the world"},{"time":566000,"text":"and exposed to your own vulnerability and fallibility"},{"time":569000,"text":"in face of, frankly, a fairly indifferent universe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574000,"text":"This is obviously an incredibly painful experience."},{"time":577000,"text":"And I think it's particularly painful for us now in the West"},{"time":580000,"text":"in the grips of what I sometimes think of"},{"time":582000,"text":"as a Control-Z culture --"},{"time":585000,"text":"Control-Z like the computer command,"},{"time":587000,"text":"undo."},{"time":589000,"text":"We're incredibly used to not having to face"},{"time":592000,"text":"life's hard realities, in a certain sense."},{"time":594000,"text":"We think we can throw money at the problem"},{"time":596000,"text":"or throw technology at the problem --"},{"time":598000,"text":"we can undo and unfriend"},{"time":600000,"text":"and unfollow."},{"time":603000,"text":"And the problem is that there are certain things that happen in life"},{"time":606000,"text":"that we desperately want to change"},{"time":609000,"text":"and we cannot."},{"time":611000,"text":"Sometimes instead of Control-Z,"},{"time":613000,"text":"we actually have zero control."},{"time":615000,"text":"And for those of us who are control freaks and perfectionists --"},{"time":619000,"text":"and I know where of I speak --"},{"time":621000,"text":"this is really hard,"},{"time":623000,"text":"because we want to do everything ourselves and we want to do it right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627000,"text":"Now there is a case to be made"},{"time":629000,"text":"that control freaks and perfectionists should not get tattoos,"},{"time":632000,"text":"and I'm going to return to that point in a few minutes."},{"time":635000,"text":"But first I want to say"},{"time":637000,"text":"that the intensity and persistence"},{"time":639000,"text":"with which we experience these emotional components of regret"},{"time":642000,"text":"is obviously going to vary"},{"time":644000,"text":"depending on the specific thing that we're feeling regretful about."},{"time":647000,"text":"So for instance, here's one of my favorite"},{"time":649000,"text":"automatic generators of regret in modern life."},{"time":653000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":655000,"text":"Text: Relpy to all."},{"time":657000,"text":"And the amazing thing"},{"time":659000,"text":"about this really insidious technological innovation"},{"time":662000,"text":"is that even just with this one thing,"},{"time":664000,"text":"we can experience a huge range of regret."},{"time":667000,"text":"You can accidentally hit \"reply all\" to an email"},{"time":670000,"text":"and torpedo a relationship."},{"time":673000,"text":"Or you can just have an incredibly embarrassing day at work."},{"time":676000,"text":"Or you can have your last day at work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":680000,"text":"And this doesn't even touch"},{"time":682000,"text":"on the really profound regrets of a life."},{"time":685000,"text":"Because of course, sometimes we do make decisions"},{"time":687000,"text":"that have irrevocable and terrible consequences,"},{"time":691000,"text":"either for our own or for other people's"},{"time":694000,"text":"health and happiness and livelihoods,"},{"time":696000,"text":"and in the very worst case scenario, even their lives."},{"time":700000,"text":"Now obviously, those kinds of regrets"},{"time":703000,"text":"are incredibly piercing and enduring."},{"time":707000,"text":"I mean, even the stupid \"reply all\" regrets"},{"time":710000,"text":"can leave us in a fit of excruciating agony for days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715000,"text":"So how are we supposed to live with this?"},{"time":718000,"text":"I want to suggest that there's three things"},{"time":720000,"text":"that help us to make our peace with regret."},{"time":723000,"text":"And the first of these"},{"time":725000,"text":"is to take some comfort in its universality."},{"time":729000,"text":"If you Google regret and tattoo,"},{"time":733000,"text":"you will get 11.5 million hits."},{"time":735000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":737000,"text":"The FDA estimates"},{"time":739000,"text":"that of all the Americans who have tattoos,"},{"time":741000,"text":"17 percent of us regret getting them."},{"time":744000,"text":"That is Johnny Depp and me"},{"time":746000,"text":"and our seven million friends."},{"time":748000,"text":"And that's just regret about tattoos."},{"time":751000,"text":"We are all in this together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":755000,"text":"The second way that we can help make our peace with regret"},{"time":757000,"text":"is to laugh at ourselves."},{"time":760000,"text":"Now in my case, this really wasn't a problem,"},{"time":762000,"text":"because it's actually very easy to laugh at yourself"},{"time":765000,"text":"when you're 29 years old and you want your mommy"},{"time":767000,"text":"because you don't like your new tattoo."},{"time":770000,"text":"But it might seem like a kind of cruel or glib suggestion"},{"time":774000,"text":"when it comes to these more profound regrets."},{"time":777000,"text":"I don't think that's the case though."},{"time":780000,"text":"All of us who've experienced regret"},{"time":783000,"text":"that contains real pain and real grief"},{"time":787000,"text":"understand that humor and even black humor"},{"time":790000,"text":"plays a crucial role in helping us survive."},{"time":793000,"text":"It connects the poles of our lives back together,"},{"time":795000,"text":"the positive and the negative,"},{"time":797000,"text":"and it sends a little current of life back into us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801000,"text":"The third way that I think we can help make our peace with regret"},{"time":804000,"text":"is through the passage of time,"},{"time":807000,"text":"which, as we know, heals all wounds --"},{"time":809000,"text":"except for tattoos, which are permanent."},{"time":813000,"text":"So it's been several years"},{"time":815000,"text":"since I got my own tattoo."},{"time":819000,"text":"And do you guys just want to see it?"},{"time":823000,"text":"All right."},{"time":825000,"text":"Actually, you know what, I should warn you,"},{"time":828000,"text":"you're going to be disappointed."},{"time":830000,"text":"Because it's actually not that hideous."},{"time":833000,"text":"I didn't tattoo Marilyn Manson's face"},{"time":836000,"text":"on some indiscreet part of myself or something."},{"time":838000,"text":"When other people see my tattoo,"},{"time":840000,"text":"for the most part they like how it looks."},{"time":842000,"text":"It's just that I don't like how it looks."},{"time":844000,"text":"And as I said earlier, I'm a perfectionist."},{"time":847000,"text":"But I'll let you see it anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854000,"text":"This is my tattoo."},{"time":858000,"text":"I can guess what some of you are thinking."},{"time":861000,"text":"So let me reassure you about something."},{"time":864000,"text":"Some of your own regrets"},{"time":866000,"text":"are also not as ugly as you think they are."},{"time":870000,"text":"I got this tattoo"},{"time":872000,"text":"because I spent most of my 20s"},{"time":874000,"text":"living outside the country and traveling."},{"time":876000,"text":"And when I came and settled in New York afterward,"},{"time":878000,"text":"I was worried that I would forget"},{"time":880000,"text":"some of the most important lessons that I learned during that time."},{"time":883000,"text":"Specifically the two things I learned about myself"},{"time":886000,"text":"that I most didn't want to forget"},{"time":888000,"text":"was how important it felt to keep exploring"},{"time":891000,"text":"and, simultaneously, how important it is"},{"time":894000,"text":"to somehow keep an eye on your own true north."},{"time":897000,"text":"And what I loved about this image of the compass"},{"time":899000,"text":"was that I felt like it encapsulated both of these ideas"},{"time":901000,"text":"in one simple image."},{"time":904000,"text":"And I thought it might serve as a kind of permanent mnemonic device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":908000,"text":"Well it did."},{"time":910000,"text":"But it turns out, it doesn't remind me of the thing I thought it would;"},{"time":913000,"text":"it reminds me constantly of something else instead."},{"time":917000,"text":"It actually reminds me"},{"time":919000,"text":"of the most important lesson regret can teach us,"},{"time":922000,"text":"which is also one of the most important lessons life teaches us."},{"time":925000,"text":"And ironically, I think it's probably the single most important thing"},{"time":928000,"text":"I possibly could have tattooed onto my body --"},{"time":931000,"text":"partly as a writer,"},{"time":933000,"text":"but also just as a human being."},{"time":935000,"text":"Here's the thing,"},{"time":939000,"text":"if we have goals"},{"time":941000,"text":"and dreams,"},{"time":943000,"text":"and we want to do our best,"},{"time":947000,"text":"and if we love people"},{"time":949000,"text":"and we don't want to hurt them or lose them,"},{"time":951000,"text":"we should feel pain when things go wrong."},{"time":955000,"text":"The point isn't to live without any regrets."},{"time":959000,"text":"The point is to not hate ourselves for having them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":963000,"text":"The lesson that I ultimately learned from my tattoo"},{"time":965000,"text":"and that I want to leave you with today"},{"time":967000,"text":"is this:"},{"time":969000,"text":"We need to learn to love"},{"time":971000,"text":"the flawed, imperfect things"},{"time":973000,"text":"that we create"},{"time":975000,"text":"and to forgive ourselves for creating them."},{"time":979000,"text":"Regret doesn't remind us that we did badly."},{"time":982000,"text":"It reminds us that we know we can do better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":985000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":987000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}